<B>__{bottom of staircase}
<A>__{just as he reaches the light something lunges at him from one side! it's the laughing man, hysterical as ever, face now seen for the first time, screeching, salivating, eyes watering. the human hyena. his grin contorts his face from ear to ear, his cackling is truly terrifying, and the hand he stretches forward has a tattoo on it (bearded anarchist's hand) a hand too big for his wrist reaching, reaching, reaching for kafka.}
